id":434762,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T15:23:01.000Z","msg":"簡易抽握手會or大寫真 步驟 by Nagisayaka <br />\n<br />\nstep 1: 有日本地址 (e.g. 轉運/日本朋友) <br />\nstep 2: 劇場盤抽選開始,選擇自己想握既mb/影既team <br />\nstep 3: submit (submit左就冇得改) <br />\nstep 4: 抽完有結果,中選同落選都會有email話你知 (<del>迷路同</del>彩就基本上一輪就滿) <br />\nstep 4.1: 第一輪通常會用黎抽晒大top先,之後再抽冇咁易爆部既mb <br />\nstep 4.2: 通常出碟之前會有幾輪抽選,完左會一次過寄比你 <br />\nstep 5: 比錢 <br />\nstep 6: 等收碟,握手/影相卷會一齊寄比你 <br />\nstep 7: 轉運收到後睇下自己仲有冇野買,冇就寄返香港 <br />\nstep 8: 收貨 <br />\nstep 9: 帶埋d卷去日本參加握手/影相會 <br />\nstep 10: 渡過愉快既一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抽NMB48個別握手會詳盡教學by DD Mr_Snowman 雪巨巴打<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://come2jp.com/idol/2016/09/21/nmb48握手會抽選方法/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcome2jp.com%2Fidol%2F2016%2F09%2F21%2Fnmb48%E6%8F%A1%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%83%E6%8A%BD%E9%81%B8%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%2F&d=BkPQdImdiDAFhis9VhRU1TA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=a7a02274\" target=\"_blank\">http://come2jp.com/idol/2016/09/21/nmb48握手會抽選方法/</a>"},{"pid":"fb74cb7de423766a500103f1e315aca14a577d6b","tid":434762,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T15:23:19.000Z","msg":"NMB48 mobile mail (モバイルメール)申請網址<br />\n<a href=\"http://sp.mail.nmb48.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsp.mail.nmb48.com%2F&d=BkPQdImdiDAFhis9VhRU1TA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=5d66f4d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sp.mail.nmb48.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n可以用credit card比錢<br />\n每日每位mb只需10.8円 港幣都係6，7毫<br />\n一齊嚟助養佢地 <br />\n<br />\n開post所需文件<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1-dn4DBQoFfSBTn2LdcjCaoi_r4hsoBOTVTzTbjvbafE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1-dn4DBQoFfSBTn2LdcjCaoi_r4hsoBOTVTzTbjvbafE&d=BkPQdImdiDAFhis9VhRU1TA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=dc3328e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1-dn4DBQoFfSBTn2LdcjCaoi_r4hsoBOTVTzTbjvbafE</a>"},{"pid":"694daae57a436c3224d205d0d3c458fada47a169","tid":434762,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T15:23:48.000Z","msg":"NMB48 Official&rlm; <br />\n@nmb48_official<br />\nFollowing<br />\nMore<br />\nいつもNMB48を応援していただき誠にありがとうございます。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">10/4(水)に発売した</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">NMB48山本彩の2ndアルバム「identity」</span>が<br />\nオリコンウィークリーCDアルバムランキングで2位となりました!!<br />\n<br />\n皆様、本当にありがとうございます！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DLwagOSV4AANe3r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDLwagOSV4AANe3r.jpg&h=e4bab682&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DLwagzlUQAAKAEq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDLwagzlUQAAKAEq.jpg&h=75c0ea39&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}